ECHO.
ECHO make the turn at the %hangout%!" %player% stared as the %vehicle% barreled
ECHO.
ECHO down the road. When %player% looked back to see %wonderdog%, the four-legged friend
ECHO.
ECHO was gone.
ECHO.
ECHO.
ECHO.
ECHO.
ECHO.
ECHO.
ECHO.
