ECHO Moments later, as the %vehicle% was about to crash into the grove, %wonderdog%
ECHO.
ECHO leaped off of the top of a large boulder and onto the top of the
ECHO.
ECHO %vehicle%. He then squeezed his way through an opening in the back of the
ECHO.
ECHO %vehicle% and found that the driver was unconscious.
ECHO.
