ECHO just inches before it reached the edge of the %hangout%. The quick-
ECHO.
ECHO thinking %wonderdog% saw that the man was not breathing and began pulling
ECHO.
ECHO him out of the %vehicle%.
ECHO.
ECHO.
ECHO.
ECHO.
ECHO.
ECHO.
ECHO.
ECHO.

REM Waits for player to push any key
PAUSE

REM Clears the screen
CLS

REM Displays story with player input
ECHO.
ECHO.
ECHO.
ECHO.
ECHO.
ECHO.
ECHO By the time %player% arrived a few minutes later, the man had
ECHO.
ECHO revived and was sitting upright on the ground, petting %wonderdog% as the
ECHO.
ECHO dog licked his face. "This here your dog?" the driver said. "Yes sir,"
ECHO.
ECHO said %player% with a great big smile. "Well, it looks like I owe you a lot.
ECHO.
ECHO Your dog just saved my life. Had he not given me CPR, I think I'd have
ECHO.
ECHO been a goner for sure!" said the driver.
