ECHO "Wow!" said %player%, running over to hug his four-legged friend. Just then
ECHO.
ECHO %wonderdog% unexpectedly leaped up, grabbing %player% by the %bodypart%, tossing %player%
ECHO.
ECHO clear of the dirt path that %player% had been running on. Moments later, a
ECHO.
ECHO big white %animal% came scurrying down that very path, and %wonderdog% the Wonder
ECHO.
ECHO Dog ran after it. "I hope that %animal% will be OK" said the driver.
