ECHO As %wonderdog% chased the %animal% down the dirt path, he started barking as if he
ECHO.
ECHO had known this %animal% from a past experience. The %animal% started to slow
ECHO.
ECHO down as if hearing a familiar sound. Moments later the %animal% had slowed
ECHO.
ECHO down to walking speed which helped %wonderdog% catch up to it. As the %animal% turned
ECHO.
ECHO around to see what was so familiar, %wonderdog% jumped off of the path and onto the
ECHO.
ECHO %animal%'s back.
