ECHO "%wonderdog%!!!" shouted the %animal% as he danced around with the little dog on his
ECHO.
ECHO back. "I'm so glad to see you again." "Me too," said %wonderdog% as he climbed down
ECHO.
ECHO back onto the dirt path. "How have you been?" questioned %wonderdog%. "I've been good,
ECHO.
ECHO just out getting in my daily run. Sorry I almost ran over your friend.
ECHO.
ECHO Sometimes I just get going and can't stop myself." said the %animal% as he
